<F P=102>   NC0704074394 Athens ATHENS NEWS in English 6 Apr 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> NC0704074394 </F>
<F P=104>  Athens ATHENS NEWS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Deputy Defence Minister Nikolaos Kouris has 
accused Turkey of attempting to change the status quo in the 
Aegean. Continuous Turkish air violations over the Aegean were 
part of "a planned escalation of tensions." Ankara's intention 
was to create false tension that could lead to a military 
confrontation and to a Pax Aegean, a peace imposed by "a foreign 
intervention" as in former Yugoslavia, the minister said 
yesterday in a state radio interview. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

