  [Excerpt] Vienna -- On the occasion of the visit by his 
South African counterpart Roelof ("Pik") Botha to Vienna, 
Foreign Minister Alois Mock has appealed to the political 
leaders in Pretoria to make violence-free elections possible. 
Austria is watching the events in South Africa with great 
