<H3> <TI>   State Condemns `Brutal Attack' on African Presidents </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    State Condemns `Brutal Attack' on African Presidents </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR0704135494 Brussels BELGA Database in French 0924 GMT 7 
Apr 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR0704135494 </F>
<F P=104>  Brussels BELGA Database </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


