<H3> <TI>   Defense Minister: Albanian Claims `Unfounded' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Defense Minister: Albanian Claims `Unfounded' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1104093394 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in 
Greek 0900 GMT 11 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1104093394 </F>
<F P=104>  Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Greek </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] National Defense Minister Yerasimos Arsenis 
described Albanian Government claims regarding a Greek 
provocation on the Greek-Albanian border as unfounded. 
Yesterday, six masked men attacked a guardpost, killed two 
Albanian soldiers, and wounded another three. 
  Government spokesman Evangelos Venizelos rejected the 
Albanian charges and stressed that Greece detests and condemns 
every act of violence and is not willing to put up with any 
provocation or any attempt to associate the Greek Government 
with such acts. 

</TEXT>

