<H4>    Cetin `Pleased' With Bosnian-Croat Progress </H4>

<F P=102> TA0804141694 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1200 
GMT 8 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0804141694 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


