<F P=100> TURKEY </F>
<H3> <TI>   Constitutional Court Decides To Close Greens Party </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Constitutional Court Decides To Close Greens Party </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1004122894 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1000 
GMT 10 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1004122894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report] </F>
  [Text] The Constitutional Court has decided to close the 
Greens Party. The Constitutional Court's decision published in 
today's edition of the OFFICIAL GAZETTE states that the Greens 
Party was closed because it did not submit the final records for 
the 1988 accounting period, although warned beforehand, within 
the statutory time period. 
  According to the Constitutional Court's decision, the assets 
of the Greens Party will be transferred to the Treasury. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

